snippet.textDisplay: I was watching this while cleaning my room and I found a letter that I wrote to you two whole years ago. I wrote it never intending to give it to you, because I never thought I would have the chance. Reading back through it, I can really see how much I’ve changed and grown since then. I’ve become more confident and more sure of myself, I started to transition socially, and I truly believe that if I hadn’t discovered this channel, none of that would have happened. Watching your videos has helped me get through some really dark times in my life, you’ve made me laugh at times when I thought I’d never smile again. You’ve worked so hard to spread a positive message to everyone and your positivity and energy has really impacted me in the most positive way. Your videos recently where you spoke about your negative feelings showed me that I’m not alone in how I’m feeling and that I can still be happy and positive. I look up to you so much and I really hope that one day I’ll be able to meet you. Thank you, Jack, for being the positive force I needed in my life to help me have a positive mental attitude💚
